{"tid":566732,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"五年遊記去過既9個國家","createTime":"2018-02-20T07:59:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-04T14:14:42.000Z","uid":100291,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"87c6ba3eb071b11bbac9076b9ec492997241aea0","tid":566732,"uid":100291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T07:59:57.000Z","msg":"五年遊記去過既9個國家<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n五年間由係香城從未用過Passpost,未去過機場,每年新年淨係返過深圳既廢青。<br />\n到依家去過幾國家,叫係睇過下世界<br />\n由跟學校,同朋友,女朋友,到依家自己一個係澳洲Working Holiday緊<br />\n發生咗好多野(睇過日本既祭典同新年,泰國潑水節,悉尼誇年....)<br />\n呢排夜晚無野做所以寫下遊記分享下<br />\n盡量一日出一兩篇到,盡量多圖小字小重複既地方<br />\n<br />\n跟國家既大致分為9章到<br />\n日本(日本最長,以前成日去)<br />\n馬來西亞<br />\n台灣<br />\n南韓<br />\n柬埔寨<br />\n泰國<br />\n越南<br />\n同埋依家既澳洲<br />\n番外:紐西蘭<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/ldTyYb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FldTyYb.jpg&h=780eef50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/gWx90F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FgWx90F.jpg&h=63b0f5e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/KiVBX1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FKiVBX1.jpg&h=2c01837b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/cU3CIV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FcU3CIV.jpg&h=7b8bceb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/XE57Ik.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FXE57Ik.jpg&h=9efcd8cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/bTrBmN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FbTrBmN.jpg&h=b5ff0f78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/metH7u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FmetH7u.jpg&h=dd4f7e6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/TWLmFS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FTWLmFS.jpg&h=46adefb9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/cf3EgH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2Fcf3EgH.jpg&h=36202029&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/QnSVDl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FQnSVDl.jpg&h=0d0470aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/Dzwjp8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FDzwjp8.jpg&h=4d0941e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/QEeUxq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FQEeUxq.jpg&h=60f4223c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/qkFMeL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FqkFMeL.jpg&h=4acaaa6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/Xvkxt6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FXvkxt6.jpg&h=a96f57a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/Vklsia.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FVklsia.jpg&h=12890689&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n9UP完,正式開波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">日本</span></span><br />\n同好多香港人一樣好鍾意既國家,成日都去-東京,名古屋,京都,米港<br />\n去睇過祭典(幾個-天神祭,祇園祭)<br />\n去東京過過新年<br />\n大阪排過福袋<br />\n京都滑過雪<br />\n沖繩潛過水睇過鯊魚<br />\n<br />\n<strong>東京</strong>-去過幾次其實我唔係特別有好感<br />\n人又多,又逼又多旅客 行起黎都好有壓力<br />\n所以我之後果幾次都係去京都(唔係大阪)<br />\n但我第第一次去同朋友,所以有點情意結<br />\n由於大家成日去,所以我會搵D特別D既講<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一次就自己去誇年順手去排APPLE福袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<strong>東京-上野30/12</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/kFuT2O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FkFuT2O.jpg&h=b0831ce6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/8b6KRZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2F8b6KRZ.jpg&h=eec3bcbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/cCGQLn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FcCGQLn.jpg&h=e9b1fb8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咖哩腐皮烏東世界第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/JkI7KC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FJkI7KC.jpg&h=4bfa52e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n出咗去行下<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/KojzPw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FKojzPw.jpg&h=ce4254fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n明治神宮<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/xGrFc5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FxGrFc5.jpg&h=703206a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雷門加Skystree<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/B8mgZk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FB8mgZk.jpg&h=44655cb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/NnZeo8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FNnZeo8.jpg&h=b732e5b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/jxezvR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FjxezvR.jpg&h=0bafa120&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/v6dBD4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2Fv6dBD4.jpg&h=50a9868b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/srPBJR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FsrPBJR.jpg&h=3816f327&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n水族館<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/5f6jX0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2F5f6jX0.jpg&h=de73b9bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/DIbeFp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FDIbeFp.jpg&h=a747f611&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/cgCAGL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FcgCAGL.jpg&h=5cf71296&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n幾型幾年前已經有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/s3eFly.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2Fs3eFly.jpg&h=96f1cab5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2014東京鐵塔<br />\n可惜去到已經閂咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/62GwqY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2F62GwqY.jpg&h=50cebc02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>鎌倉+江之島</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/W62MuC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FW62MuC.jpg&h=c09e1409&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/eUxRu3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FeUxRu3.jpg&h=b665f80b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/NsZUgl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FNsZUgl.jpg&h=27c2d4b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/qdyln4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2Fqdyln4.jpg&h=deb3f6d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/h01gFz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2Fh01gFz.jpg&h=4309c8aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/ArUuYh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FArUuYh.jpg&h=250baf41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢塊野好好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/eMSvxB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FeMSvxB.jpg&h=cecfbe69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n成島都係貓<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/vNJwDz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FvNJwDz.jpg&h=14c84cf3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/NohCu7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FNohCu7.jpg&h=fe1cf2df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/vjEsc1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FvjEsc1.jpg&h=078bc919&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/h5tDV7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2Fh5tDV7.jpg&h=c6872789&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/8z3Y4H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2F8z3Y4H.jpg&h=a73c1453&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/sRfPKq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FsRfPKq.jpg&h=a32189a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/cwC35r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FcwC35r.jpg&h=ec4100d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"color: red;\">重頭戲 雷門新年倒數</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n行過已經有人排緊福袋(2/1先開賣)<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/gPJqQz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FgPJqQz.jpg&h=73397a37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n排隊祈福<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/6jg0lM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2F6jg0lM.jpg&h=353d9909&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n未到時間周圍行<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/LUCW2g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FLUCW2g.jpg&h=04732df8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/UANJop.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FUANJop.jpg&h=d4588e05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/qHCBRv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FqHCBRv.jpg&h=fb64b606&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/JHP58E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FJHP58E.jpg&h=fa5a8705&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/LBXxjH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FLBXxjH.jpg&h=a6aea1cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/B2oVjW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FB2oVjW.jpg&h=8d5c62f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/fM6G4u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FfM6G4u.jpg&h=6219abac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/HIaAmn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FHIaAmn.jpg&h=8b3cb526&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/3bdxFl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2F3bdxFl.jpg&h=18921744&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/VyAKmk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FVyAKmk.jpg&h=08aa3832&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n倒數時<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實無咩特別,我搵番條片再PO<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/4cJ6qm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2F4cJ6qm.jpg&h=2c276334&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n傳說中既「除夕鳴鐘」108響<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/Zjc8I6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FZjc8I6.jpg&h=3b2683f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/NRABJV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FNRABJV.jpg&h=8b40b07f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n影完比佢嚇親<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/xc87ge.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2Fxc87ge.jpg&h=4ea3eb26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n東京咁就完咗,因為我1/1我就狗衝咗去大阪<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/y5PkWs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2Fy5PkWs.jpg&h=9da9248a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0e44f9263fd636d541f719a90b1b52feafc68c21","tid":566732,"uid":100291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T08:43:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5a2ac2344025391a88df7b3e62c65b18c0b9afd","tid":566732,"uid":100291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T09:25:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30047ef72d2d456a8e760c5f4c6275c46af8948b","tid":566732,"uid":100291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T10:37:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8152a1579a393138ed8c70d67a3e2bcafee0335","tid":566732,"uid":30927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T10:54:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65a66a6b7609166113c2c65b9365ea1e0cc13379","tid":566732,"uid":73311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T12:50:38.000Z","msg":"留名待睇!"},{"pid":"192c0b829c7abacdccb61ed5a676fb068df02fcb","tid":566732,"uid":100291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T01:32:26.000Z","msg":"收工再po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee906cd96f9fecb91f3444204e142fcd0d0d9e50","tid":566732,"uid":145307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T01:44:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1faec7356f07bbfe2d69ec7c2685439aa562b51e","tid":566732,"uid":47187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T02:00:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"829da0f81ef8c28f089765aa12ce9d4a9ad6c281","tid":566732,"uid":33777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T02:11:57.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"b9c9eb6612778139f189f323a8c99f5e03f00cb9","tid":566732,"uid":127347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T03:49:56.000Z","msg":"我都鍾意去京都大阪多啲，東京節奏又人多太似香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60c4ea9e40021f9c5c9471947476f8b205de6d0d","tid":566732,"uid":100291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9c9eb6612778139f189f323a8c99f5e03f00cb9","tid":566732,"uid":127347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T03:49:56.000Z","msg":"我都鍾意去京都大阪多啲，東京節奏又人多太似香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T04:17:06.000Z","msg":"東京買野都嫌佢逼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n野又貴過關西"},{"pid":"7796ecd3c1f853441393d3a0efa4b6197c7d4a7f","tid":566732,"uid":100291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T05:42:51.000Z","msg":"1/1 我倒完數就坐新幹線去大阪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n排APPLE福袋(福袋=新年禮物包)<br />\n好可惜依家好似無再出啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n富士山<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/L2Em8W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FL2Em8W.jpg&h=df3ea92e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中間經過中部好大雪<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/cC5WiJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FcC5WiJ.jpg&h=f7bbcbb8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>大阪</strong></span></span>-比東京舒服(心齋橋除外)<br />\n一落車就去咗心齋橋排Apple既福袋<br />\n已經好多人<br />\n要登記<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/reRxgM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FreRxgM.jpg&h=6c98c392&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/xbPzwn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FxbPzwn.jpg&h=a5ff0203&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n登記完同前面後面傾掂就輪住出去行下食飯<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/coQUPi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FcoQUPi.jpg&h=fb137b7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仆你個街落雨雪,凍撚到<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/bd8PNE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2Fbd8PNE.jpg&h=507c8bf2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/SIlaqN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FSIlaqN.jpg&h=efb931bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n結果......<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgc.appbank.net/c/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Lucky-Bag-20151-9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgc.appbank.net%2Fc%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F01%2FLucky-Bag-20151-9.jpg&h=288a0b68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(我太嬲無影到,所以呢張係我之後搵返黎)<br />\n屌你排足兩日,得部<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">iPod touch</span></span> (2018年仲用緊)<br />\n嬲撚到我跳起<br />\n<a href=\"http://ringhk.com/news2.php?id=7861\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fringhk.com%2Fnews2.php%3Fid%3D7861&d=O5GDw088ZA10p07MbgUQiTOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=a2c08c5e\" target=\"_blank\">http://ringhk.com/news2.php?id=7861</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">之後我就去咗京都,係到依家我最愛既地方</span></span><br />\n之後我會出個長篇係祭典<br />\n不過之前就出下相,冬天既先<br />\n青水寺<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/15AbdW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2F15AbdW.jpg&h=83cac636&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/BIUK3p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FBIUK3p.jpg&h=ed53c2aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/1xbaZR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2F1xbaZR.jpg&h=775c37d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/H3OLwW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FH3OLwW.jpg&h=c739736b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢個位其實唔洗錢係另一邊就行到上黎<br />\n下次去大家可以試下,又唔洗入去逼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/kbsmny.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2Fkbsmny.jpg&h=00237748&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n八坂神社-<br />\n我成日去既神社(因為京都既祇園祭係係八坂神社)<br />\n祭典果部份我再講<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/mnXfPy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FmnXfPy.jpg&h=1e620d30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新年人山人海<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/Vr65aP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FVr65aP.jpg&h=7832d258&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n行咗去鴨川<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/KkwTCg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FKkwTCg.jpg&h=10449ab1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第二日開始就去咗志賀滑雪(離京都40分鐘地鐵)<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/XKPu4w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FXKPu4w.jpg&h=e6f9e6d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/5B0PmC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2F5B0PmC.jpg&h=14599267&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/5ZTSUi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2F5ZTSUi.jpg&h=e8284b88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/jdiqEQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FjdiqEQ.jpg&h=69749399&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如果又唔想坐咁耐車去,又想睇靚景<br />\n志賀係一個唔錯既選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n下一遍我就講關西兩個大祭典<span style=\"color: gold;\">(天神祭同祇園祭)</span>,同埋我一個月既祭典之旅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/s2mzPl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2Fs2mzPl.jpg&h=390609a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/8afP2c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2F8afP2c.jpg&h=f84c0087&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1ba91908903387360ce8d03eabcbc0d5447526da","tid":566732,"uid":41562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T06:12:04.000Z","msg":"留名待丁貴"},{"pid":"8104e973fcf73ee59a6e9192cfafeacefb6c601c","tid":566732,"uid":75540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T06:50:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"063badc7fe2aaab2540d68e95c52882469624bfd","tid":566732,"uid":100291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T10:35:46.000Z","msg":"打兩個大祭典之前就Post下D 小祭典先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為其實前前後後都去咗4-5個祭典<br />\n<br />\n大阪-七夕祭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我去咗四天王寺既七夕祭典<br />\n日本既七夕同我地差不多由來都係牛郎和織女咁,但佢地後來改成貴族眺望星空吟詩作樂既宮廷活動,再變變下就寫紙條向星星許願<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢地既係七夕似慶祝活動多過用黎溝女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n毒到好似得我一個去都唔驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n夏天太熱門口會灑水<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/QtcuqE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FQtcuqE.jpg&h=e5b47a18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢上邊D掛飾幾靚<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/IJm3s2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FIJm3s2.jpg&h=bf19065b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有人表演太鼓,好型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/4CfktZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2F4CfktZ.jpg&h=31e5b70f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/MSvGLI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FMSvGLI.jpg&h=9cd65f08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/UaIxCF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FUaIxCF.jpg&h=ae333936&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n各種祭典野食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然會比平時貴小小,但好有特色平時出邊好難搵到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/NC5iJc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FNC5iJc.jpg&h=289695a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/VIpvjg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FVIpvjg.jpg&h=5ba4ebe4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/rAuOGv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FrAuOGv.jpg&h=0871ed88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小朋友係到點燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/S5jM6x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FS5jM6x.jpg&h=8a7ce0e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n愈夜愈好睇<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/6SkXad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2F6SkXad.jpg&h=63e1ddf5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/vj2IEp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2Fvj2IEp.jpg&h=bb9fa5c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/AprJSv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FAprJSv.jpg&h=0370dbb8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我當時既願望,好在依家都順順利利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/57j32R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2F57j32R.jpg&h=158be142&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁又一日之後就返咗青旅休息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/zbmVqP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FzbmVqP.jpg&h=90616ac8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽日應該Post埋另一個七夕祭既慶祝活動就講去京都既祭典<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我想搵好D資料先 唔想求其出垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8ecfdd110d8ab22bb51abb578a762660862e49f","tid":566732,"uid":100291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T10:38:02.000Z","msg":"大家有咩想問都可以嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家係澳洲返工好撚悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"875db2853568c10ebc6450d8b216901e8bb39242","tid":566732,"uid":100291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T22:33:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6cd18d4de68f27457944872239