g&h=6127bb59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黃昏既時間<br />\n對面係色費區<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/jM45RT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FjM45RT.jpg&h=48d664d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n來啦來啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/UC7NFa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FUC7NFa.jpg&h=2aa4d9db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我影相唔靚,所以大家見諒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但現場睇真係好靚好感7<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/iynE0M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FiynE0M.jpg&h=9f0a867a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/DCcT1V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FDCcT1V.jpg&h=a014ed7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/M6UEG2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FM6UEG2.jpg&h=44c36ee0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/agP3zf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FagP3zf.jpg&h=4ecb09a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n下一篇終於要講京都既<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">祇園祭</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/czZTeW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FczZTeW.jpg&h=57aac93e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由於太多所以我會跟佢活動講<br />\n我用兩個星期去咗前半部份,無撚得輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5fb8ae7f1e32d3d673555cb50032ace1e4f4d36","tid":566732,"uid":33777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T09:16:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e106a114121f0600cbd412829fed409c1c213